    dc:description "FIG. 2. (A, B) Acryptolaria sp., hydrothecae; (C–F) Filellum antarcticum (Hartlaub, 1904), hydrothecae; (G, H) Filellum magnificum sp. nov., hydrothecae. (A from ANT II-4 Stn 450; B from ANT IX-3 Stn 207; C, D from neotype; E from ANT VIII-5 Stn 16-403; F, H from ANT VIII-5 Stn 16-481; G from ANT II-4 Stn 502.) Scale bar: 500 Mm (A, B); 200 Mm (C–H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5250388/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5250396>
    dc:description "FIG. 5. Filellum magnificum sp. nov. (A) General view of a coppinia; (B) egg and gonothecal apertures; (C) detail of gonothecal aperture. (All photographs from holotype.)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5250396/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

